{"parse":{"title":"OPOJAZ","pageid":3820410,"revid":826046766,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>OPOJAZ</b> (\u041e\u041f\u041e\u042f\u0417) (<a href=\"/wiki/Russian_language\" title=\"Russian language\">Russian</a>: <span lang=\"ru\">\u041e\u0431\u0449\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u0438\u0437\u0443\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u041f\u043e\u044d\u0442\u0438\u0447\u0435\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u042f\u0437\u044b\u043a\u0430</span>, <i><b>O</b>b\u0161\u010destvo izu\u010denija <b>PO</b>\u00e8ti\u010deskogo <b>JAZ</b>yka</i>, \"Society for the Study of Poetic Language\") was a prominent group of <a href=\"/wiki/Linguistics\" title=\"Linguistics\">linguists</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Literary_critic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Literary critic\">literary critics</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/St._Petersburg\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"St. Petersburg\">St. Petersburg</a> founded in 1916 and dissolved by the early 1930s.  The group included <a href=\"/wiki/Viktor_Shklovsky\" title=\"Viktor Shklovsky\">Viktor Shklovsky</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Boris_Eikhenbaum\" title=\"Boris Eikhenbaum\">Boris Eikhenbaum</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Osip_Brik\" title=\"Osip Brik\">Osip Brik</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/Yury_Tynianov\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yury Tynianov\">Yury Tynianov</a>.  Along with the <a href=\"/wiki/Moscow_linguistic_circle\" title=\"Moscow linguistic circle\">Moscow linguistic circle</a> it was responsible for the development of <a href=\"/wiki/Russian_formalism\" title=\"Russian formalism\">Russian formalism</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Literary_semiotics\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Literary semiotics\">literary semiotics</a>.  It was dissolved under political pressure as \"formalism\" came to be a political term of opprobrium in the Soviet state.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bibliography\">Bibliography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=OPOJAZ&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Bibliography\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><i>\u0412. \u0411. \u0428\u043a\u043b\u043e\u0432\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.opojaz.ru/manifests/kakpriem.html\">\u0418\u0441\u043a\u0443\u0441\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u043a\u0430\u043a \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0435\u043c</a> (in <a href=\"/wiki/Russian_language\" title=\"Russian language\">Russian</a>: <span lang=\"ru\">Russian</span>)</li>\n<li><i>\u0411. \u041c. \u042d\u0439\u0445\u0435\u043d\u0431\u0430\u0443\u043c</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.opojaz.ru/manifests/kaksdelana.html\">\u041a\u0430\u043a \u0441\u0434\u0435\u043b\u0430\u043d\u0430 \u00ab\u0428\u0438\u043d\u0435\u043b\u044c\u00bb \u0413\u043e\u0433\u043e\u043b\u044f</a> (in <a href=\"/wiki/Russian_language\" title=\"Russian language\">Russian</a>: <span lang=\"ru\">Russian</span>)</li>\n<li><i>\u041e. \u0412\u0430\u043b\u044c\u0446\u0435\u043b\u044c</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.opojaz.ru/walzel/index.html\">\u041f\u0440\u043e\u0431\u043b\u0435\u043c\u0430 \u0444\u043e\u0440\u043c\u044b \u0432 \u043f\u043e\u044d\u0437\u0438\u0438</a> (in <a href=\"/wiki/Russian_language\" title=\"Russian language\">Russian</a>: <span lang=\"ru\">Russian</span>)</li>\n<li><i>\u041b. \u0414. \u0422\u0440\u043e\u0446\u043a\u0438\u0439</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.opojaz.ru/critique/trotsky.html\">\u0424\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0448\u043a\u043e\u043b\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u044d\u0437\u0438\u0438 \u0438 \u043c\u0430\u0440\u043a\u0441\u0438\u0437\u043c</a> (\u0433\u043b\u0430\u0432\u0430 \u0438\u0437 \u043a\u043d\u0438\u0433\u0438 \u00ab\u041b\u0438\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0443\u0440\u0430 \u0438 \u0440\u0435\u0432\u043e\u043b\u044e\u0446\u0438\u044f\u00bb, 1923) (in <a href=\"/wiki/Russian_language\" title=\"Russian language\">Russian</a>: <span lang=\"ru\">Russian</span>)</li>\n<li><i>\u0411. \u041c. \u042d\u0439\u0445\u0435\u043d\u0431\u0430\u0443\u043c. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.opojaz.ru/method/method_intro.html\">\u0422\u0435\u043e\u0440\u0438\u044f \u00ab\u0444\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043c\u0435\u0442\u043e\u0434\u0430\u00bb</a> (in <a href=\"/wiki/Russian_language\" title=\"Russian language\">Russian</a>: <span lang=\"ru\">Russian</span>)</i></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Handshake_(Workshop_Cologne_%2706).jpeg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Handshake_%28Workshop_Cologne_%2706%29.jpeg/30px-Handshake_%28Workshop_Cologne_%2706%29.jpeg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Handshake_%28Workshop_Cologne_%2706%29.jpeg/45px-Handshake_%28Workshop_Cologne_%2706%29.jpeg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Handshake_%28Workshop_Cologne_%2706%29.jpeg/60px-Handshake_%28Workshop_Cologne_%2706%29.jpeg 2x\" data-file-width=\"690\" data-file-height=\"688\" /></a></td><td><i>This article about a <a href=\"/wiki/Linguistics\" title=\"Linguistics\">linguistics</a> organization is a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Stub\" title=\"Wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help Wikipedia by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=OPOJAZ&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a>.</i><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 15px; display: none;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Ling-org-stub\" title=\"Template:Ling-org-stub\"><abbr title=\"View this template\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Ling-org-stub\" title=\"Template t